giving the Lady Vols a chance to win their seventh national championship.
National player of the year Tamika Catchings picked it up after scoring just two
points in the first half and freshman Kara Lawson hit two big shots to lead
Tennessee (33-3) into Sunday night's title game. The Lady Vols will play
Connecticut or Penn State, who met in the second semifinal.
</P>
